            <div id="mission-content" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
              <h2 class="page-content-subheader">Mission</h2>
              <hr class="page-content-divider" />
              <p>The DXKB is intended to provide an integration of curated data, tools, and AI models that aid in accelerating research and shortening the development time for creating vaccines for emerging viruses, consistent with the <a href="https://cepi.net/cepi-20-and-100-days-mission" target="_blank">CEPI 100 days mission</a>.</p><br>
              <p>
                To achieve this, DXKB integrates high quality structured bioinformatic data, literature data, experiments, AI models, and other related information for select viral families of interest and their close relatives.
                The resource also serves as starting point for research into the development of Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) models for accessing scientific data, and the development of agentic workflows for answering complex scientific questions.
              </p>
            </div>

